 not speak of them or act upon them.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6664, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 127 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34930,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/01\/14\/tawhid-dominion-spending\/","url_meta":{"origin":23037,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Tawhid: Allah\u2019s dominion not decreased by spending","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 14, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe hand of Allah is full and it is not diminished by continuous spending night and day. Do you not see that He has been spending since the creation of the heavens and the earth, and\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15810,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/08\/23\/hour-dua-friday\/","url_meta":{"origin":23037,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Jumuah: Special hour for Friday supplications","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 23, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, mentioned the day of Friday and he said, \u201cIn it is a moment in which no Muslim stands to pray and ask Allah for something but that he will be given it,\"\u00a0and he indicated with his hand\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &